## Add to QodeX

Edit `~/.qodex/config.yaml`:

```yaml
mcp:
  servers:
    {{NAME}}:
      command: node
      args: ["{{ABSOLUTE_DIST_PATH}}/index.js"]
      enabled: true
```

Then restart QodeX or run `/mcp-restart {{NAME}}`.

