## Adding tools

1. Create `src/tools/<your-tool>.ts` exporting a `Tool` schema and a handler.
2. Import it in `src/index.ts`, add to the `TOOLS` array, and add a dispatch case.
3. `npm test` — write a vitest that exercises the handler directly.

## Layout

```
src/
  index.ts            Server entry — sets up transport + dispatcher
  tools/
    example.ts        One file per tool (schema + handler)
test/
  example.test.ts     Pure unit tests on the handler
```
